因此美官員亦加劇其憂慮，尤其是在美軍定期對在當地進行系統測試。以色列議員Ram Ben-Barak則表示，並沒有任何針對中國或長和，但如果盟友美國對此項目感到擔憂，則應該重新檢視項目細節。"},{"pid":"e31ea060039426fc663d9b9041621a424bbbddfe","tid":2029534,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"收得個廿億息不如跟我地炒股仲好"},{"pid":"1373cadb10751214659e54cca737f906d800d768","tid":2029534,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55c4073b3343e9a05a92113b65fe0df436a0071a","tid":2029534,"uid":77959,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"509ffbe4f9fe467313e94c0f7493c017d0433de1","tid":2029534,"uid":49699,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9219726fa0ce4f0e3ac1c3b9d58fdbe14d8884d3","tid":2029534,"uid":41308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"其實李氏家族係度撤資中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"撤左好多年... 佢未必夠馬雲有錢, 但佢比馬雲早好知道共產黨信唔過走人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:43:32.000Z","msg":"佢點會唔夠馬雲有錢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錢幾多倍都唔知啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:51:56.000Z","msg":"馬雲身家高過誠哥了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4571e6c56e5bb53c132a63e139f7336accdc96","tid":2029534,"uid":316329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"誠哥係香港炒牛熊應該捱唔到3日"},{"pid":"ae69aed905ce634334763e75196f816d928fbe63","tid":2029534,"uid":161222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"割肉餵鷹<br />\n<br />\n聽過未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d429a91288e349072ebfd76e1492555b4e0c406","tid":2029534,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep